name: Dinari JNJ
description: The Dinari JNJ dShares token (JNJ.d) represents 1:1 ownership of shares in Johnson & Johnson, a global healthcare leader known for its innovations in pharmaceuticals, medical devices, and consumer health products. Each JNJ.d token is fully backed by a corresponding Johnson & Johnson share held securely in a transparent and auditable treasury. By leveraging blockchain technology, JNJ.d provides seamless access to Johnson & Johnson stock, enabling 24/7 trading, fractional ownership, instant settlement, and enhanced liquidity.
